    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 《特里修斯之门》将经典roguelike的残酷无情与广阔开放世界RPG的自由深度融为一体。</p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 探索一个广袤的、程序生成的世界，这里不会有任何指引。你将需要运用你全部的技巧和战略才能，来征服这片变幻莫测的神秘界域“埃纳利亚”中的远古地下城、阵营军队和游荡巨兽。</p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1519490/extras/c98a7f6fa7dd20f5853c91f8e66d42e4.poster.avif?t=1768224502\" width=616 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1519490/extras/c98a7f6fa7dd20f5853c91f8e66d42e4.webm?t=1768224502\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1519490/extras/c98a7f6fa7dd20f5853c91f8e66d42e4.mp4?t=1768224502\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1519490/extras/371f08fdb16e8640cfcd6073c14de19c.avif?t=1768224502\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1519490/extras_big/371f08fdb16e8640cfcd6073c14de19c.avif?t=1768224502 width=800 height=98 /></span></p> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>随机生成</strong>：每次冒险都是独一无二的，因为城镇、地下城和世界地图在每次游戏开始时都会重新生成。</p></li> <li> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>探索</strong>：在一个广阔而危险的世界中航行，生存是关键。建立营地，觅食求生，并管理你的疲劳以在荒野中坚持下去。世界地图上的每一个格子都可以探索，并且会随时间推移而持续存在。</p></li> <li> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>交战阵营</strong>：随着阵营为领土而战，世界地图上的区域会不断演变。这些冲突会影响一个地区的繁荣度，从而影响其定居点中可用的商品和任务。加入战斗以影响最终结果。</p></li> <li> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>多样的敌人类型</strong>：超过100种独特的敌人类型，拥有定制的AI，将挑战你的技巧和适应能力。</p></li> <li> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>充满挑战的地下城</strong>：在8种独特的地下城类型中考验你的勇气，每种都有自定义的布局和房间类型，包括城堡、洞穴、要塞、藏身处和神殿。</p></li> </ul> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1519490/extras/f4b03875bee1afc70b2a0f5af297cf7c.avif?t=1768224502\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1519490/extras_big/f4b03875bee1afc70b2a0f5af297cf7c.avif?t=1768224502 width=800 height=98 /></span></p> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>回合制战斗</strong>：我们的计时单位制时间系统为回合制战斗带来了全新的变化。回合的优先顺序取决于你的移动、武器速度和行动速度，强调了战术决策的重要性。</p></li> <li> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>战斗选项</strong>：使用超过200种战斗技能和12种武器技能类型来定制你的策略，每种都有独特的游戏风格。</p></li> <li> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>地下城事件</strong>：这个世界充满了生机，有时，地下城中会触发特殊事件，需要你敏捷的思维，或许还需要你后脑勺也长着眼睛！</p></li> <li> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>技能</strong>：体验14种非战斗技能，如医疗、炼金术、军需学、运动和阅读。通过使用和策略性地分配专精点数来提升技能等级，解锁技能和被动效果，根据你的游戏风格定制你的角色。</p></li> </ul> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1519490/extras/a27d36539adb869a398d0813408e67ce.poster.avif?t=1768224502\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1519490/extras/a27d36539adb869a398d0813408e67ce.webm?t=1768224502\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1519490/extras/a27d36539adb869a398d0813408e67ce.mp4?t=1768224502\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1519490/extras/1a2a1ae27af053d808026442874e05ce.avif?t=1768224502\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1519490/extras_big/1a2a1ae27af053d808026442874e05ce.avif?t=1768224502 width=800 height=98 /></span> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>丰富的战利品</strong>：数百种物品，包括药剂、护甲、配方和可在游戏中阅读的传说典籍。偶然发现稀有的附魔，或学习亲手为你的物品附魔。</p></li> <li> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>任务系统</strong>：完成任务以获得奖励并提高你在当地人中的声望，从而解锁专属福利。除了手工设计的任务外，城镇和城市还会根据每个城镇中非玩家角色的职责生成动态任务。</p></li> <li> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>深度制作系统</strong>：制作食物、药剂和药品；使用分解得来的材料升级和维护你的护甲。通过购买或寻找配方卷轴来提升你的制作技能。</p></li> <li> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>角色定制</strong>：通过7种背景选择和超过30种初始特性来塑造你的角色命运。</p></li> </ul> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1519490/extras/0a0a825f61cfc14ccc4c7ced2dae32b4.poster.avif?t=1768224502\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1519490/extras/0a0a825f61cfc14ccc4c7ced2dae32b4.webm?t=1768224502\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1519490/extras/0a0a825f61cfc14ccc4c7ced2dae32b4.mp4?t=1768224502\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p> <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >常见问题解答</h2><strong>通关游戏需要多长时间？</strong> <i>游戏目前已包含大量内容。通常需要20-30小时才能通关，此外还有更多内容等待探索。</i><br><strong>游戏是否使用了AI绘画？</strong> <i>所有的游戏美术、音效和音乐都由人类艺术家创作。</i> <br><strong>游戏更新频率如何？</strong> <i>我们会定期更新，大多数更新大约每月一次。游戏已经历了数十次重大更新，未来还会有更多。</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1519490/extras/31adaebc94ea0b6bc06e83004d6f4b93.poster.avif?t=1768224502\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1519490/extras/31adaebc94ea0b6bc06e83004d6f4b93.webm?t=1768224502\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://